{"tid":1777658,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【評論最精彩系列】多名女孩被輸送給當地人大代表、富商 這只是#河北遷安性侵案#的冰山一角","createTime":"2019-12-10T11:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T11:34:46.000Z","uid":231132,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"082e4656754e51b0ee889982539bc76b60ce2db3","tid":1777658,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"2018年3月，河北省遷安市警方抓獲了一個長期&ldquo;碰瓷&rdquo;的犯罪團伙。 審訊過程中又發現了更嚴重的罪行&mdash;&mdash;該團伙成員曾輪姦數名未成年少女，並強迫她們賣淫賺錢。 遷安市公安局黨委副書記康永卻坐不住了，他給負責查辦團伙案件的民警塞錢，希望他們不再繼續偵查。 這一舉動為他招來了法網。  <br />\n<br />\n2018年7月，康永因行賄被唐山市監委留置調查，隨後主動交代，自己也牽涉其中，性侵未成年女孩。 警方偵查中發現，牽涉其中的人還有遷安市人大代表王雙。<br />\n<br />\n有知情人透露，康永、王雙的落網僅揭開了遷安性侵案的冰山一角，該案疑有數十名涉案人，其中包括公職人員、富商、人大代表等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4447873166499200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.weibo.cn%2Fdetail%2F4447873166499200&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cef4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=a6481de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.weibo.cn/detail/4447873166499200</a><br />\n<br />\n請問微博有沒有負責人🤯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/waVRJiG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwaVRJiG.jpg&h=a0ed5eed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MfTG5w2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMfTG5w2.jpg&h=1015e88e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a835c2ad7f36100bd65c83728eb78a995251d8b","tid":1777658,"uid":288523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0990d0495cf27c7899750c9163d98c3dbb8d2c4","tid":1777658,"uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a835c2ad7f36100bd65c83728eb78a995251d8b","tid":1777658,"uid":288523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"Errr 可能係「沉默的大多數」"},{"pid":"dd4c2871d06a05125d1fb9f1197e7104e8bfb066","tid":1777658,"uid":165683,"like":